            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>CSS files placed in the document head block rendering by default. CSS loaded asynchronously via JavaScript or placed at the end of the body typically does not block rendering.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
