            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes. Non-critical CSS can be loaded asynchronously using media query tricks or JavaScript techniques like loadCSS. Critical above-the-fold CSS should be inlined in the HTML head rather than deferred.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
